wxPython Cookbook
Chapter 11 Responsive Interfaces, Using Threads and Timers
Recipe 4 Using Timers

This is the example code for Recipe 4 Using Timers

Prerequisites:

1) Python 2.5 or 2.6 has been installed
2) wxPython 2.8 has been installed for the version of Python used above

How to run this script:

From the command line or your IDE run the following command

python timers.py
